5,649 975w,https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2025/02/3.-Add-flour-and-chocolate-81c46f7.jpg?quality=90&amp;fit=1000,666 1000w"><img class="image__img" src="https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2025/02/3.-Add-flour-and-chocolate-81c46f7.jpg?quality=90&amp;fit=700,466" alt="Mixing flour, chopped chocolate and cookie dough" data-item-name="Mixing flour, chopped chocolate and cookie dough" title="3.-Add-flour-and-chocolate" style="aspect-ratio:1 / 0.6661290322580645;object-fit:contain" loading="lazy" width="700" height="466.2903225806452"></picture></div></div></div></li><li class="method-steps__list-item"><h3 class="method-steps__item-heading heading-5">step 4</h3><div class="editor-content"><p>Scoop 10 large tbsps of the mixture onto the trays, leaving enough space between each to allow for spreading.</p><div class="image chromatic-ignore"><div class="image__container" style="max-width:700px"><picture class="image__picture" width="700" height="466.2903225806452"><source type="image/webp" sizes="(min-width: 992px) 940px,(min-width: 768px) 728px,(min-width: 544px) 556px,calc(100vw - 20px)" srcset="https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2025/02/5.-Cookie-dough-on-tray-v2-4cf784f.jpg?quality=90&amp;webp=true&amp;fit=325,216 325w,https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2025/02/5.-Cookie-dough-on-tray-v2-4cf784f.jpg?quality=90&amp;webp=true&amp;fit=375,250 375w,https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2025/02/5.-Cookie-dough-on-tray-v2-4cf784f.jpg?quality=90&amp;webp=true&amp;fit=650,433 650w,https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2025/02/5.-Cookie-dough-on-tray-v2-4cf784f.jpg?quality=90&amp;webp=true&amp;fit=750,500 750w,https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2025/02/5.-Cookie-dough-on-tray-v2-4cf784f.jpg?quality=90&amp;webp=true&amp;fit=975,649 975w,https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2025/02/5.-Cookie-dough-on-tray-v2-4cf784f.jpg?quality=90&amp;webp=true&amp;fit=1000,666 1000w"><source sizes="(min-width: 992px) 940px,(min-width: 768px) 728px,(min-width: 544px) 556px,calc(100vw - 20px)" srcset="https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2025/02/5.-Cookie-dough-on-tray-v2-4cf784f.jpg?quality=90&amp;fit=325,216 325w,https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2025/02/5.-Cookie-dough-on-tray-v2-4cf784f.jpg?quality=90&amp;fit=375,250 375w,https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2025/02/5.-Cookie-dough-on-tray-v2-4cf784f.jpg?quality=90&amp;fit=650,433 650w,https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2025/02/5.-Cookie-dough-on-tray-v2-4cf784f.jpg?quality=90&amp;fit=750,500 750w,https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2025/02/5.-Cookie-dough-on-tray-v2-4cf784f.jpg?quality=90&amp;fit=975,649 975w,https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2025/02/5.-Cookie-dough-on-tray-v2-4cf784f.jpg?quality=90&amp;fit=1000,666 1000w"><img class="image__img" src="https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2025/02/5.-Cookie-dough-on-tray-v2-4cf784f.jpg?quality=90&amp;fit=700,466" alt="Five cookie dough balls on a lined tray" data-item-name="Five cookie dough balls on a lined tray" title="5.-Cookie-dough-on-tray-v2" style="aspect-ratio:1 / 0.6661290322580645;object-fit:contain" loading="lazy" width="700" height="466.2903225806452"></picture></div></div></div></li><li class="method-steps__list-item"><h3 class="method-steps__item-heading heading-5">step 5</h3><div class="editor-content"><p>Bake for 10-12 mins or until firm at the edges but still soft in the middle – they will harden a little as they cool.</p><div class="image chromatic-ignore"><div class="image__container" style="max-width:700px"><picture class="image__picture" width="700" height="466.2903225806452"><source type="image/webp" sizes="(min-width: 992px) 940px,(min-width: 768px) 728px,(min-width: 544px) 5