 tray" data-item-name="Five cooked chocolate chip cookies on a tray" title="Easy chocolate chip cookies" style="aspect-ratio:1 / 0.6661290322580645;object-fit:contain" loading="lazy" width="700" height="466.2903225806452"></picture></div></div></div></li><li class="method-steps__list-item"><h3 class="method-steps__item-heading heading-5">step 6</h3><div class="editor-content"><p>Leave to cool on the tray for a few mins before eating warm, or transfer to a wire rack to cool completely. <em>Will keep for three days in an airtight container.</em></p><div class="ad-placement" data-count="661"></div></div></li></ul>
